ricas%2Fbrazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl%2Findex.html&h=216c3621\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/08/23/americas/brazil-beef-amazon-rainforest-fire-intl/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當大家打緊國際輸出革命，全球各國都幫緊香港人發聲既時候，另一單近期最大既新聞就係亞馬遜森林火燭，而香港竟然係入口最多牛肉既地方？？？<br />\n<br />\n唔該，依家香港軟實力啱啱先建立到，出國同人講自己係香港人，人地都會知你係民主鬥士，你唔會想又加返條破壞環境既罪名呀嘛？ 就算無人怪香港人，依個都係再次展現香港人人性光輝既重要機會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">即刻發起戒食牛肉行動！！！！<br />\n以示香港人面向國際，對國際社會既責任感！！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e105a084fe117e238679b6c9e0783da8691b3831","tid":1505844,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:12:58.000Z","msg":"幾號返？"},{"pid":"f55fc2de238f5e961b9b248837ac6cc60743ca86","tid":1505844,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823e3c9795264bde8222f5d5fc2395076561213c","tid":1505844,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"eb1a662503a5d98cb96413b74e0ce6aaadbb99b4","tid":1505844,"uid":135445,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"中大之光<br />\n香港之光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db9d8c9bb8202dfcdc944e1de155f3f2e73d1d9","tid":1505844,"uid":119135,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"為國爭光"},{"pid":"5c3