,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:56:40.000Z","msg":"我記得俾人叫Hong Kong, China已經唔係第一年嘅事，幾年前已經係咁<br />\n聽過好多國家嘅隊都問點解支那會有兩隊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW香港人好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e45c7bd615a86f10fd3e5504a89e4ae6c6b6d6","tid":1505844,"uid":206812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"家母一路睇電視 見好多人爬山嘅時候<br />\n俾狗咬住個背囊走唔甩 咬到好傷好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以用師奶思想 建議大家<br />\n行山嘅時候 個書包入面裝水裝紙巾好喇<br />\n至於你啲身分證 或者其他重要嘢<br />\n有腰包就放腰包（要戴係面衫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裡面</span></span>啊懵佬）<br />\n無就好似呀婆咁 著條有袋/拉鍊嘅背心底衫喇<br />\n你知啲動物好鍾意咬住個袋唔放 唔俾你走<br />\n只要你個袋無重要嘢 就可以嚟一招<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">金蟬脫殼</span></span>"},{"pid":"41212b7784c7d2e63b63fce166c53c6072df51f6","tid":1505844,"uid":15883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a9f9d8271c394ae440fcd2ce0d5d195ae28714","tid":1505844,"uid":81160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:12:04.000Z","msg":"有無暴大同學話我知係咪全香港人出賽"},{"pid":"c96eb226f60157a0ce945a7b69a55c79cd9ef5f9","tid":1505844,"uid":155079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:20:01.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"3f3a56f6e6c192047787a96031759fe1a31fa42f","tid":1505844,"uid":62512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/